        public TableColumnInfoDTO getTableColumnInfoDTOByName(java.lang.String name)
        Gets the TableColumnInfoDTO object for table column in this table which is not deleted and has the given name. Performs a case insensitive search for table column name.
        Parameters:
        name - String the name of the table column to be searched.
        Returns:
        TableColumnInfoDTO table column info DTO for the table column with the given in this table, returns null if no such table column is found.

      • checkTableColumnName

        public boolean checkTableColumnName(java.lang.String tableColumnName)
        Checks if the table column name provided is already in use by some other table column in this table or not. Performs a case insensitive search on the table column name.
        Parameters:
        tableColumnName - String the name of the table column to checked for availability.
        Returns:
        boolean, true if the provided name is not taken by any other existing table column, false otherwise.
